sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant BC as Browser Client
    participant JS as Socket.IO JS
    participant SO as Flask-SocketIO
    participant RM as RoutesManager
    participant DB as MultiHomeDBManager

    BC->>BC: użytkownik klika toggle
    BC->>JS: emit 'toggle_device' {device_id, home_id}
    JS->>SO: transport Socket.IO → serwer
    SO->>RM: wywołaj handler 'toggle_device' (session, data)
    RM->>RM: waliduj uprawnienia (user ∈ home)
    RM->>DB: MultiHomeDBManager.toggle_device(home_id, device_id, user_id)
    DB->>DB: UPDATE devices SET state = NOT state WHERE id=... AND home_id=...
    DB-->>RM: zwróć device_data
    RM->>RM: CacheManager.invalidate_cache(f"home:{home_id}:devices")
    RM->>BC: emit 'device_updated' do inicjującego klienta (potwierdzenie)
    BC-->>BC: aktualizuj UI lokalnie
    RM->>RM: _broadcast_device_update(home_id, device_data)
    RM->>SO: emit 'device_updated' do sesji każdego użytkownika gospodarstwa
    SO-->>BC: inni klienci otrzymują 'device_updated'
    BC-->>BC: aktualizuj DOM (document.querySelector...)

